---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTAButton from "../components/CTAButton.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — TT Motorcycle School"
  description="With over 22 years of expertise, TT Motorcycle School is a trusted, DVSA-approved training centre in Sussex offering CBT, A1, A2 and Direct Access courses with quality personal tuition."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section__eyebrow">Who We Are</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">
        Trusted, Expert Motorcycle Training in Sussex
      </h1>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">
        Over 22 years of experience. DVSA-approved. Small class sizes. The same
        instructor from your first lesson to your test day.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-grid">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Welcome to TT Motorcycle School</h2>
        <p>
          With over 22 years of industry expertise — including directing the <em
            >Get On</em
          > feature at Motorcycle Live (Birmingham NEC) — TT Motorcycle School is
          a premier, long-established training centre. We specialise in comprehensive
          motorcycle and scooter training, offering CBT, A1, A2, and Direct Access
          Scheme (DAS) courses designed to help you confidently take to the road.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Locations</h2>
        <p>
          Our administrative headquarters is located in <strong>Hassocks</strong
          >, while our dedicated CBT training pad is situated in <strong
            >Brighton</strong
          >. Both locations offer easy access via car or public transport, with
          free allocated parking for students.
        </p>

        <h2>DVSA-Approved, Quality Personal Tuition</h2>
        <p>
          Led by our founder, Alan, all tuition is delivered by a carefully
          selected team of RoSPA and DVSA-approved motorcycle instructors. We
          pride ourselves on providing Quality Personal Tuition — a standard
          often lost at larger, high-volume schools.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our commitment to safety, thorough instruction, and skill development
          has earned us a highly respected reputation with examiners at local
          DVSA test centres.
        </p>

        <h2>The TT Motorcycle School Difference</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Consistent Guidance:</strong> You will train with the same dedicated
            instructor from your first lesson straight through to your test day.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Small Class Sizes:</strong> We guarantee a maximum student-to-instructor
            ratio of 2:1, ensuring your learning is never diluted and your safety
            remains our top priority.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Real-World Route Training:</strong> All road and Module 2 tuition
            takes place on the roads in and around Sussex, using reliable radio systems
            for constant communication. We train directly on the test routes near
            the Burgess Hill and Eastbourne multi-purpose test centres.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Comprehensive Support:</strong> Our dedicated office team is always
            available via phone, email, or in person to provide professional, honest,
            and knowledgeable advice.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          At TT Motorcycle School, we combine hard work, industry expertise, and
          a genuine commitment to helping you achieve your riding goals.
        </p>

        <div style="margin-top: var(--space-8);">
          <CTAButton
            href="/cbtbooking/"
            label="Book Your Training"
            variant="accent"
            size="md"
          />
          &nbsp;&nbsp;
          <CTAButton
            href="/contact/"
            label="Get in Touch"
            variant="primary"
            size="md"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar__card sidebar__card--plain">
          <h3 class="sidebar__title">Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar__info-list">
            <li><strong>Experience:</strong> 22+ years in the industry</li>
            <li>
              <strong>Locations:</strong> Hassocks (admin) &amp; Brighton (training)
            </li>
            <li><strong>Approved by:</strong> DVSA &amp; RoSPA</li>
            <li><strong>Courses:</strong> CBT, A1, A2, DAS, Refresher</li>
            <li>
              <strong>Class size:</strong> Maximum 2:1 student/instructor ratio
            </li>
            <li><strong>Bikes provided:</strong> Yes</li>
            <li>
              <strong>Parking:</strong> Free allocated parking at both sites
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-10);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    }
  }

  .sidebar__card {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }

  .sidebar__card--plain {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .sidebar__title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .sidebar__info-list {
    list-style: none;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .sidebar__info-list strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    display: block;
  }

  .prose a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
